_sText: <font face="helvetica" color="#6666FF">A remake of dm_bloodbath.  I added some new halls and I brightened the map up considerably.  It used to be too dark to play which is why I remade it.  I also randomized the spawns in this  version so server admins don't need to edit them.  It's got them set already.  There are 64 spawns in this version.</font>
